page.title: 11Wildlife near Aston Cantlow
page.content: The wildlife around Aston Cantlow is very abundant.In the last two years I have made a list of all the mammals I have seen. This is my list of mammals and rodents;-Fox,Common shrew,Water shrew,Hedgehog,Mole,Brown rat,Water vole,Bank vole,House Mouse,Harvest Mouse,Grey Squirrel, Stoat,Weasel,Badger, Rabbits and Hares. I have been studying butterflies. Butterflies are uncommon now but I have made a list of butterflies;-Large white,Cabbage white,Small white,Black Veined white,Peacock,Orange tip, Brimstone,Small Tortoiseshell,Large Tortoiseshell,Red Admiral,Meadow Brown ,Wall Brown and Holly Blue.I also made a list of moths;_Cinnbar Moth,Orange tip,White Ermine,Garden Tiger, Brimstone moth and the six spot Burnet.
